    • Method Detail

      • processPacket

        void processPacket(Object producer,
                 IPacketWrapper packet)
                   throws LibavException
        Send a packet to the consumer. The consumer should free the packet after use. The producer should not send one packet to multiple consumers.
        Parameters:
        producer - packet producer
        packet - a packet
        Throws:
        LibavException - if an error occurs
